com.alex323glo.spacex.dao

Class Dao<Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alex323glo.spacex.dao.Dao<Model>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccessTokenDaoJSON, UserDaoJSON

    public abstract class Dao<Model>
extends java.lang.Object
    Data Access Object (DAO) interface for needed com.alex323glo.spacex.model. This interface gives access to CRUD operations with system's DB (Create, Read, Update and Delete operations). Generic is used to make interface for flexible for any types of system's data models (such as User).
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    alex323glo
    See Also:
    Model, User
